psalm.text:
[[Ps 9,8]]The LORD sits enthroned forever; 
he has set up his throne for judgment.
[[Ps 9,9]]He judges the world with justice;
he governs the peoples with equity.

[[Ps 9,10]]The LORD is a stronghold for the oppressed, 
a stronghold in times of distress.
[[Ps 9,11]]They trust in you who cherish your name, 
for you forsake not those who seek you, O LORD.

[[Ps 9,12]]Sing praise to the LORD enthroned in Zion; 
proclaim among the nations his deeds;
[[Ps 9,13]]for the avenger of blood has remembered; 
he has not forgotten the cry of the poor.
